data.description: Just under 10 acres with good fences. Very nice home with great living space and tons of storage. Large living and office just off driveway access. Efficient kitchen with gas cooking, walk in corner pantry, refrigerator stays. Master suite is down and bath has just been remodeled and updated. Spacious secondary bedrooms upstairs plus extra closets and attic storage access. Detached 4 car garage with one bay set up as a workshop including a second refrigerator. Barn has electricity. RV parking with hookups. Exterior motion activated security cameras.Rent includes water, septic, trash,propane for cooking,internet. Tenant pays electric.8 acres pasture will allow 8 large animals.Pets case by case.No smoking
